snippet.title: The Game of Life: SpongeBob SquarePants Edition - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Join SpongeBob and friends in the 3D spongified version of the classic LIFE board game! Enjoy hilarious micro-games as you find your dream job, collect your paychecks, buy your dream home, and more!

Developed by Sarbakan and released for the long-defunct Nick Arcade, this game saw a physical release in the USA thanks to none other than THQ. Yes, you read that right! The very same THQ who would be ressurected by Nordic Games AB (now known as Embracer Group) as THQ Nordic and go on to publish Battle For Bikini Bottom: Rehydrated and Cosmic Shake.

THQ and THQ logo (C) THQ Nordic / Embracer Group
